These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: amber, green
1. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who likes green##1
2. the person who likes green is not to the right of the person who likes green##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Color   | green | amber |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, helicopter
1. the person driving the train is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the train is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Transport   | helicopter | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different games are played: monopoly, bridge
1. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the left of the person playing bridge##5
2. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
3. the person playing monopoly is not to the right of the person playing monopoly##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Game   | monopoly | bridge |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-4::.
